{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/go-gorm/gorm/issues/1205","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/go-gorm/gorm","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/go-gorm/gorm/issues/1205/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/go-gorm/gorm/issues/1205/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/go-gorm/gorm/issues/1205/events","html_url":"https://github.com/go-gorm/gorm/issues/1205","id":180444125,"node_id":"MDU6SXNzdWUxODA0NDQxMjU=","number":1205,"title":"mssql: Invalid usage of the option NEXT in the FETCH statement","user":{"login":"dipbhi","id":12301512,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjEyMzAxNTEy","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/12301512?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/dipbhi","html_url":"https://github.com/dipbhi","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dipbhi/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dipbhi/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dipbhi/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dipbhi/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dipbhi/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dipbhi/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dipbhi/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dipbhi/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dipbhi/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"labels":[],"state":"closed","locked":false,"assignee":null,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":11,"created_at":"2016-10-01T07:41:55Z","updated_at":"2020-01-06T15:26:55Z","closed_at":"2017-02-22T00:28:20Z","author_association":"NONE","type":null,"active_lock_reason":null,"sub_issues_summary":{"total":0,"completed":0,"percent_completed":0},"issue_dependencies_summary":{"blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"When executing First or Limit + Find with mssql, a sql server error is generated\n\nError\n\n> mssql: Invalid usage of the option NEXT in the FETCH statement.\n\nIn these cases sql query being executed is invalid\nQuery\n\n> SELECT \\* FROM \"users\"  WHERE \"users\".deleted_at IS NULL AND ((\"users\".\"id\" = '1')) ORDER BY \"users\".\"id\" ASC FETCH NEXT 1 ROWS ONLY\n\nBasically the query needs to have \"OFFSET 0 ROWS FETCH NEXT 1 ROW ONLY\", or the FETCH statement should be removed all together.\n\nEnvironment: Windows 10, MS Sql Server Express 2016\n\nHere is the sample code:\n\n```\npackage main\n\nimport (\n    \"log\"\n\n    \"github.com/jinzhu/gorm\"\n\n    _ \"github.com/jinzhu/gorm/dialects/mssql\"\n)\n\ntype User struct {\n    gorm.Model\n    Email     string\n    Firstname string\n    Lastname  string\n}\n\nfunc main() {\n    // db connection code goes here\n    db, err := gorm.Open(\"mssql\", /*conn string*/)\n    if err != nil {\n        log.Panic(err)\n        return\n    }\n    defer db.Close()\n\n    db.LogMode(true)\n\n    id := 1\n    var e1 User\n    db.First(&e1, id) // generates error\n    log.Println(\"user id: \", e1.ID)\n\n    var e2 User\n    db.Offset(0).Limit(1).Find(&e2, id) // genertes error\n    log.Println(\"user id: \", e2.ID)\n}\n```\n","closed_by":{"login":"jinzhu","id":6843,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjY4NDM=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/6843?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/jinzhu","html_url":"https://github.com/jinzhu","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jinzhu/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jinzhu/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jinzhu/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jinzhu/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jinzhu/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jinzhu/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jinzhu/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jinzhu/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jinzhu/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/go-gorm/gorm/issues/1205/reactions","total_count":2,"+1":2,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/go-gorm/gorm/issues/1205/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"completed"}